{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260627_past_time_reply_should_not_commit_001","name":"时间未确认时回复不能承诺先看局","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"manual_feedback_20260627_past_time_reply_logic","observed_at":"2026-06-27T16:35:00+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","时间歧义","回复逻辑","禁止过早承诺","guard"],"text":"下午两点 0.5 无烟杭麻，一缺三，帮我组一桌","sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","expected":{"now":"2026-06-27T16:00:00+08:00","suggested_reply_contains":["两点","明天"],"forbidden_in_suggested_reply":["可以，我先帮你看","我先帮你看","先帮你看","帮你看"],"outbox_count":0,"candidate_search_called":false},"actual":{"suggested_reply":"可以，我先帮你看。你说的两点是明天吗，还是改其他时间？ 你一个人吗？","problem":"既然开局时间还不确定，系统不能说“我先帮你看”。这会让老板看起来已经开始查局/摇人，但后端实际应该停在确认时间。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"过期时间/上午下午歧义场景下，_follow_up_text 只返回确认问题，不再添加“可以，我先帮你看”；技能库和 golden dataset 增加禁止项。","regression_refs":[{"type":"boss_trial_golden","id":"past_start_time_requires_confirmation_001"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_llm_bad_past_time_reply_is_guarded_before_display"}]}
