{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260628_afternoon_4pm_over_asks_ampm_001","name":"下午业务语境下4点不应追问上午下午","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"manual_feedback_20260628_afternoon_4pm","observed_at":"2026-06-28T13:59:00+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","时间消歧","置信度门禁","后端规则过死"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"4点无烟0.5，173，5h"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"你觉得现在是凌晨两点吗？"}],"expected":{"first_turn":{"start_time":"16:00","missing_fields":[],"suggested_reply_exact":"好的，我帮你问问。","outbox_count_min":1,"forbidden_in_suggested_reply":["上午还是下午","明天","改其他时间"]},"architecture":"不要新增具体 badcase if-else；由时间候选、当前业务语境和置信度阈值决定是否推进。"},"actual":{"first_turn":{"suggested_reply":"你说的4点是上午还是下午？"},"second_turn":{"suggested_reply":"你说的4点是明天吗，还是改其他时间？"},"problem":"系统把所有上午/下午歧义一律升级为关键缺失，导致当前已经下午且候选时间明显是16:00时仍机械追问。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"新增通用 time_resolution_policy：只在候选时间为今天、接近未来、当前已进入下午业务语境且置信度超过阈值时清除上午/下午歧义；后端仍负责状态机、工具权限和置信度门禁；补充 boss_trial_golden 和单测。","regression_refs":[{"type":"boss_trial_golden","id":"afternoon_numeric_time_resolves_to_same_day_001"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_afternoon_numeric_time_resolves_to_same_day_without_hardcoded_badcase"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260628_gender_mix_preference_all_female_candidates_001","name":"用户要求一男一女但候选池全是女性","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"manual_feedback_20260628_gender_mix","observed_at":"2026-06-28T14:30:00+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","候选推荐","用户画像","性别组合","软约束","badcase"],"text":"4点无烟0.5，4h，272，最好再来一男一女","sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","expected":{"candidate_preference_genders":["male","female"],"candidate_gender_sequence":["male","female"],"candidate_search_called":true,"invite_text_should_not_disclose":["一男一女","男","女"],"architecture":"不要把具体话术写成 if-else；将性别作为客户画像字段，将一男一女作为候选组合软约束进入 search_candidate_customers 的排序。"},"actual":{"problem":"客户画像没有结构化 gender 字段，推荐器也没有候选组合偏好，导致只按玩法/档位/时间/烟况分数排序，页面前排全是女性名字。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"customers 表新增 gender 字段并回填 mock 画像；解析候选组合偏好写入 game notes 和 parsed.candidate_composition_preference；search_candidate_customers query 记录组合偏好；推荐器在基础分排序后优先选出男+女组合；候选邀约不透露性别偏好；新增 boss_trial_golden 和单测。","regression_refs":[{"type":"boss_trial_golden","id":"candidate_gender_composition_preference_001"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_candidate_recommendation_respects_soft_gender_composition_preference"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260628_candidate_da_stale_272_after_prior_confirm_001","name":"前一位候选人已确认后，下一位打！仍回复272","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260628151206_9a0ca860","observed_at":"2026-06-28T15:12:00+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","候选人回复","状态推进","进度标签","LLM guard","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"liu","sender_name":"刘姐","text":"可以"},{"sender_id":"amy","sender_name":"Amy","text":"打！"}],"expected":{"first_candidate":{"feedback_type":"accepted","progress_label_after":"272","suggested_reply":"好的，加你272了。"},"second_candidate":{"feedback_type":"accepted","confirmed_before":1,"confirmed_after":2,"progress_label_after":"人齐","suggested_reply":"好的，人齐了。","outbox_status":"已确认"},"forbidden_second_reply":["加你272了","待确认"]},"actual":{"second_candidate":{"feedback_type":"candidate_question","progress_label_after":"272","suggested_reply":"好的，加你272了。","outbox_status":"待确认"},"problem":"“打！”被后端分类成待确认，LLM 又生成了带状态推进含义的“加你272了”，导致既没有确认 Amy，又把上一轮进度标签误用于下一轮回复。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"候选人回复分类将“打/打！”纳入 accepted；非 accepted/arrived 场景 guard 禁止 LLM 输出加你、371、272、173、人齐等状态推进话术；accepted 场景要求 LLM 回复中的进度标签和后端计算的 fallback 一致，不一致则回退到后端安全回复；新增 candidate_message 端到端单测。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_candidate_acceptance_word_da_updates_progress_after_prior_confirmation_and_guards_llm"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_candidate_message_accepts_invite_reports_272_after_first_join"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260629_contextual_slots_not_materialized_001","name":"LLM已补齐多轮槽位但后端未物化局对象","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260629230829_b24bf41e","observed_at":"2026-06-29T23:08:29+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","多轮对话","上下文管理","槽位物化","受控agent","候选人搜索"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"通宵0.5有人吗"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"组一个"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"人齐开吧，有烟无烟都行"}],"expected":{"semantic_action":"create_game","start_time_mode":"people_ready","duration_mode":"overnight","rules_contains":["人齐开","通宵","烟况都可"],"candidate_search_called":true,"send_message_called":true,"outbox_count_min":1,"suggested_reply_exact":"好的，我帮你问问。"},"actual":{"semantic_resolution":{"proposed_action":"create_game","confidence":0.85,"slots":{"level":"0.5","start_time_mode":"people_ready","duration_mode":"overnight","smoke":"any","known_players":1,"missing_count":3}},"backend_validation":{"effective_action":"ask_clarification","code":"missing_game_context"},"suggested_reply":"现在没有现成的局，要不要帮你组一个？","problem":"LLM 已正确理解当前消息是在补上一轮组局条件，但后端只信规则解析出的 game；当前轮 parsed_game 为空时没有把 previous_game + slots 合成可校验局对象，导致候选人搜索和待审批邀约没有执行。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"新增 contextual_game_materialization：当 LLM 高置信提出 create_game 且存在上一轮工作流上下文时，后端将 previous_game 和 LLM slots 合成为 GameRequest，再继续状态机、缺字段、工具权限和 outbox 审批；新增 fake LLM 回归测试。","regression_refs":[{"type":"controlled_workflow_regression","id":"controlled_multiturn_slot_fill_001"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_truncated_followup_semantic_action_still_reaches_candidate_tools"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260629_single_word_group_confirmation_hidden_missing_slots_001","name":"上一轮问要不要组一个，本轮回复组后被错误降级为留意","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260629233806_525e3685","observed_at":"2026-06-29T23:38:06+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","多轮对话","短答确认","上下文管理","guard","缺字段","受控agent"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"通宵有人吗"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"组"}],"expected":{"semantic_action_proposed":"create_game","if_critical_slots_complete":{"candidate_search_called":true,"send_message_called":true,"suggested_reply_exact":"好的，我帮你问问。"},"if_critical_slots_missing":{"effective_action":"ask_clarification","missing_fields_not_empty":true,"forbidden_suggested_reply":["好的，我先帮你留意下。"]}},"actual":{"semantic_resolution":{"proposed_action":"create_game","confidence":0.85,"reply_text":"好的，帮您组一个通宵局。您想打什么玩法？财敲还是川麻？档位有偏好吗？"},"backend_validation":{"effective_action":"create_game"},"tool_results":{"search_candidate_customers_called":false,"send_message_called":false},"reply_draft_llm":"好的，我帮你问问。","displayed_suggested_reply":"好的，我先帮你留意下。","problem":"后端把 LLM 的上下文确认组局识别为了 create_game，但未先按关键槽位重新校验；随后又因咨询现有局分支把 missing_fields 清空，导致回复模型误以为信息足够，最后 guard 因没有 outbox 把“帮你问问”降级为“留意下”。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"create_game 语义提案即使来自 LLM，也必须先经过关键槽位校验；若是上一轮组局确认短答且槽位不足，不能进入咨询现有局的 missing_fields 清空分支，而是返回真实缺字段并自然追问；补充短答“组”的回归测试。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_single_word_group_confirmation_with_complete_context_reaches_candidate_tools"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_contextual_group_one_without_game_context_asks_clarification_not_waiting"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260630_missing_slots_pool_no_match_reply_001","name":"确认组局后缺字段却回复现在没有要组一个吗","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260630083136_09b97d11","observed_at":"2026-06-30T08:31:36+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","多轮对话","回复生成","缺字段优先级","guard","受控agent"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"早麻有人吗"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"可以"}],"expected":{"second_turn":{"semantic_action_proposed":"create_game","effective_action":"ask_clarification","missing_fields_not_empty":true,"suggested_reply_should_ask_any_of":["几点","多大","烟","几小时"],"forbidden_suggested_reply":["现在没有诶，要组一个吗？","要组一个吗"]}},"actual":{"second_turn":{"semantic_action_proposed":"create_game","effective_action":"ask_clarification","missing_fields":["start_time","stake","smoke","duration"],"llm_reasoning":"追问三个关键字段：时间、档位、烟况，符合最多问3个问题的限制。","suggested_reply":"现在没有诶，要组一个吗？"},"problem":"回复生成提示词把 search_current_open_games 无匹配的规则放在缺字段之前，导致已经确认组局但缺关键信息时仍套用“现在没有，要组一个吗”。guard 也没有拦截这种“已确认组局后又问是否组”的矛盾话术。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"回复生成优先级调整为 missing_fields 非空时必须先自然追问；现有局无匹配话术仅适用于 missing_fields 为空且用户只是咨询现有局；guard 新增缺字段场景拦截 pool no match 回复和未覆盖缺字段的回复；新增端到端回归测试。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_boss_trial_observability.py::test_missing_slots_guard_blocks_pool_no_match_reply_after_group_confirmation"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_reply_policy.py::test_reply_policy_clarification_asks_missing_slots_only"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260702_autonomous_agent_internal_count_leak_001","name":"Agent回复泄露已问候选人数","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260702225905_e2a7c680","observed_at":"2026-07-02T22:59:27+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","全自动agent","工具结果可见性","上下文管理","外发边界","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","text":"无烟也可以"}],"expected":{"architecture":"不要通过不断追加话术 if-else 或正则止血；工具结果必须做可见性分级，LLM只拿到agent_observation和customer_visible_facts，候选人数、草稿数、outbox等进入private_facts或审计日志。","suggested_reply_should_not_disclose":["问了8个人","8位候选人","8份草稿","待审批","outbox"],"suggested_reply_style":"简短自然，例如：好的，按这个要求帮你问了，有消息跟你说。"},"actual":{"suggested_reply":"好的张哥，我已经帮你把要求改成无烟也可以，重新帮你问了8个人，有消息了通知你。","problem":"autonomous agent 上下文把完整工具结果和 outbox_count/candidate_count 回喂给模型，模型把内部执行指标当成客户可见信息复述。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"将 autonomous agent 的工具结果回喂改为 visibility_contract，区分 agent_observation、customer_visible_facts、private_facts_not_for_customer；scratch_summary 从具体计数改为布尔状态；提示词要求客户回复只使用 customer_visible_facts；未新增坏话术正则或业务 if-else。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_autonomous_agent.py::test_autonomous_agent_does_not_feed_private_outbox_counts_to_model"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_autonomous_agent.py::test_autonomous_agent_tool_result_prompt_marks_internal_counts"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260702_autonomous_agent_availability_without_tool_evidence_001","name":"未查当前局池却回复通宵有的","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260702231415_f8489e16","observed_at":"2026-07-02T23:14:15+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","全自动agent","工具证据契约","当前局池","幻觉","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","conversation_id":"test01","text":"通宵有人吗"}],"expected":{"architecture":"不要针对“通宵有人吗”写 if-else；当前有没有局/有没有人/能不能拼属于外部事实，必须由 search_current_open_games 工具提供证据。","required_tool_before_reply":"search_current_open_games","forbidden_without_tool_evidence":["通宵有的","有的","没有","暂时没有","有一个局"],"if_no_matches_reply_style":"现在没有通宵局，要组一个吗？"},"actual":{"agent_step":{"decision":"wait_user","intent":"inquire_existing_game","tool_name":null,"reply_text":"通宵有的，你几个人？打什么档位？"},"context":{"open_games":[],"tool_results":[]},"problem":"模型声明 intent=inquire_existing_game，但没有调用 search_current_open_games，直接对当前局池事实作出“通宵有的”的判断。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"新增 autonomous agent 工具证据契约：intent=inquire_existing_game 且没有成功的 search_current_open_games 工具结果时，模型的 wait_user/final_reply 不可直接落地，运行时转为 search_current_open_games 工具调用；工具结果再以 visibility_contract 回喂模型。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_autonomous_agent.py::test_autonomous_agent_forces_current_game_search_before_availability_reply"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260702_autonomous_agent_slow_stiff_followup_001","name":"通宵补充人数和金额后回复慢且上一轮追问僵硬","source":"boss_trial_console_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_20260702232230_5198b05e","observed_at":"2026-07-02T23:22:30+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","全自动agent","多轮对话","延迟预算","工具计划","话术风格","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","conversation_id":"boss_trial","text":"通宵有人吗"},{"sender_id":"assistant","sender_name":"系统建议","conversation_id":"boss_trial","text":"你几个人，打什么档位？"},{"sender_id":"zhang","sender_name":"张哥","conversation_id":"boss_trial","text":"一个人，1块的"}],"expected":{"architecture":"不要把具体话术写成 if-else；通过 Agent 输出协议支持批量工具计划，通过提示词约束客户可见话术风格。","tool_plan":"当已经确认要组局且没有条件分支时，允许模型一次提出 create_game -> search_candidate_customers -> create_pending_outbox，后端仍逐个校验权限、幂等、状态机和审批边界。","reply_style":{"forbidden_words":["档位","槽位","候选人","待审批","工具","检索","匹配分"],"preferred_examples":["你这边几个人？打多大？","0.5还是1？","好的，我帮你问问。"]},"latency_expectation":"无条件分支的工具链不应每个工具都消耗一次 LLM 往返。"},"actual":{"trace_summary":{"llm_calls":5,"elapsed_seconds":23,"final_reply":"好的，按这个要求帮你问了，有消息跟你说。"},"problem":"模型理解正确并推进了完整工具链，但一工具一轮 LLM 导致响应慢；上一轮追问使用“档位”这类后台词，老板话术不自然。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"Agent 输出协议新增 tool_calls 批量工具计划；后端按顺序执行并逐个做权限、幂等、状态机校验，只有所有工具成功且 goal_status=completed 时才使用同轮 reply_text；提示词新增客户话术风格约束，禁止后台词，金额询问改为“打多大/0.5还是1/几块的”。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_autonomous_agent.py::test_autonomous_agent_executes_batch_tool_plan_without_extra_llm"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260704_candidate_flexible_duration_reply_001","name":"候选人询问烟况和时长时回复系统化，没有收集时长偏好","source":"agent_runtime_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_69939f947171","observed_at":"2026-07-04T13:35:34+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","agent_runtime","候选人回复","话术风格","弹性条件","上下文管理","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"wang01","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"下午有局吗？"},{"sender_id":"assistant","sender_name":"系统建议","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"下午有一个杭麻0.5的局，人齐开，要加入吗？"},{"sender_id":"wang01","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"可以，有烟还是无烟啊，打多久呢？"}],"expected":{"reply_style":"像麻将馆老板一样回答已知条件并收集未定偏好。","reply_example":"烟都可以，打多久还不确定，你想打多久呢？","semantic_rule":"duration_kind=flexible 不能客户可见地写成“时长灵活”，应表达为时长还没定，并追问候选人想打多久。","forbidden_reply_contains":["时长灵活","烟不限","你看行不","系统","草稿","候选人"]},"actual":{"final_reply":"这个局烟不限，时长灵活，人齐开。你看行不？","problem":"主模型把内部槽位 duration_kind=flexible 和 smoke_preference=any 直接总结成系统化话术，没有把“打多久呢”识别为候选人偏好收集问题。审查模型只负责信息泄露，没有拦截这类运营话术质量问题。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"在主提示词增加内部槽位到自然老板话术的翻译准则：any -> 烟都可以，asap_when_full -> 人齐开，flexible -> 时长还没定；候选人询问弹性条件时优先收集候选人偏好。新增当前主链路 regression 样本。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_system_prompt_requires_customer_visible_reply_self_check"},{"type":"agent_runtime_regression","id":"runtime_candidate_asks_flexible_duration_001"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260704_identity_question_leaks_organizer_role_001","name":"客户问张哥是谁时泄露张哥是组局人","source":"agent_runtime_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_f0f53020dfd1","observed_at":"2026-07-04T13:37:43+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","agent_runtime","隐私边界","关系画像","候选人回复","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"wang01","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"下午有局吗？"},{"sender_id":"assistant","sender_name":"系统建议","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"下午有一个杭麻0.5的局，人齐开，要加入吗？"},{"sender_id":"wang01","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"可以的"},{"sender_id":"wang01","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"张哥是谁"}],"expected":{"reply_style":"不要主动泄露局内角色，优先回答人物关系。","reply_example":"你们之前没打过。","privacy_rule":"发起人、参与者、已确认状态默认不是当前用户可见信息；客户问某人是谁，不等于授权暴露他是发起人。","relationship_profile_needed":["played_together_count","avoid_playing"],"forbidden_reply_contains":["组这个局的人","发起人","局主","组织者","已确认","候选人"]},"actual":{"final_reply":"张哥是组这个局的人。","problem":"主模型直接使用 active_games.organizer_name 暴露发起人角色；审查模型只检查候选名单和后台流程，没有把发起人/参与者身份默认不可见纳入审查标准。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"新增 CustomerRelationship 关系画像；上下文注入 sender_relationships；search_customers 根据 organizer_id/existing_player_ids 参考关系画像避开 avoid_playing；主提示词和审查提示词补充发起人/参与者身份默认不可见原则；新增当前主链路 regression 和 pytest。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_context_includes_sender_relationships_for_active_game"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_search_customers_avoids_known_pair_conflicts"},{"type":"agent_runtime_regression","id":"runtime_identity_question_uses_relationship_not_role_001"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260704_existing_game_reply_stiff_field_copy_001","name":"现成局回复把结构化字段直接拼给客户，话术僵硬","source":"agent_runtime_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_6404827b66be","observed_at":"2026-07-04T13:53:31+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","agent_runtime","话术生成器","现成局查询","客户可见文本","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"wang02","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"现在有人打牌吗"}],"expected":{"architecture":"主 Agent 负责决策和工具调用；独立话术生成器把可见事实转成麻将馆老板口吻；审查模型只做泄露和未发生动作兜底。","reply_example":"有个173，1块有烟，人齐开，打吗？","style_rules":["1 不应直接和有烟拼成“1有烟”，应说“1块有烟”","有匹配局时不要同时塞入“要不要加入/还是自己组一个”这种选择过载","不主动透露发起人身份；no_prior_play_record 时只说公共局条件"],"forbidden_reply_contains":["1有烟","要帮你问问能不能加进去，还是你自己组一个","发起人","审批","草稿"]},"actual":{"final_reply":"现在有一个1有烟、人齐开、4小时的局，要帮你问问能不能加进去，还是你自己组一个？","problem":"主模型查到局池后把工具结果中的结构化摘要直接拼进客户回复，审查器只删除隐私泄露，不负责把字段味话术改成老板口吻。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"新增 customer_visible_text_generation 话术生成环节：主模型输出 action 后、客户可见审查前，对 reply_to_user、create_invite_drafts/create_outbound_message_drafts 中的 message_text 做独立 LLM 合同改写；prompt 定义信息分层、金额/烟况/人齐开/173 等自然表达；新增 pytest 覆盖当前回复和候选人邀约文本。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_customer_visible_text_generation_rewrites_reply_before_review"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_customer_visible_text_generation_rewrites_invite_text_before_review_and_draft"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260704_requesting_customer_not_counted_as_player_001","name":"发起组局客户未计入参与人数，导致回复还差人数错误","source":"agent_runtime_user_feedback","trace_id":"trace_9d80de97b12b","observed_at":"2026-07-04T14:18:47+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","agent_runtime","状态建模","参与人计数","话术生成器","审查边界","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"zhang01","sender_name":"张哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"帮我组个财敲1块有烟人齐开"},{"sender_id":"wang04","sender_name":"王","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"打"},{"sender_id":"wang04","sender_name":"王","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"张哥不是人吗？"}],"expected":{"state_model":"麻将馆老板是系统运营方；找老板帮忙组局的客户是首位玩家，默认要打，必须计入 participants 和人数。","reply_example":"算的，加上你两个，还差两个。","forbidden_reply_contains":["张哥是组局的","他还没说打不打","目前确认的就你一个","还差3个","organizer","participants"],"copywriting_rule":"客户可见回复默认不要在开头带客户姓名或微信备注。"},"actual":{"final_reply":"张哥是组局的，但他还没说打不打，目前确认的就你一个，还差3个，人齐了通知你。","problem":"Game.organizer_id 被模型当成发起客户，但 store.create_game 没有把发起客户放入 participants；审查器据此认为张哥未确认，导致人数被算成1缺3。话术生成器还保留了过多姓名和角色描述。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"create_game 统一通过 normalize_game_participants 把发起客户作为 requester/joined 参与者；SQLite 读取旧 game payload 时也修复缺失 requester 的视图；主提示词明确 organizer_id 是兼容字段，代表发起客户/首位玩家而不是老板；话术生成器默认不在开头带客户姓名，追问某人算不算人时只回答人数；审查提示词允许回答计数但禁止泄露组局人/发起人角色。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_create_game_counts_requesting_customer_as_player"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_sqlite_create_game_counts_requester_and_repairs_legacy_payload"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_customer_visible_text_generation_prompt_defines_boss_tone_and_visibility_layers"}]}
{"schema_version":1,"kind":"badcase","id":"badcase_20260704_copywriter_over_infers_public_facts_001","name":"话术生成器越权新增人数和关系事实","source":"agent_runtime_user_feedback","trace_id":"manual_feedback_20260704_copywriter_boundary","observed_at":"2026-07-04T15:05:00+08:00","tags":["老板反馈","agent_runtime","话术生成器","语义保真","上下文边界","badcase"],"turns":[{"sender_id":"wang02","sender_name":"王哥","conversation_id":"runtime_trial","text":"现在有人打牌吗"}],"expected":{"architecture":"话术生成器只做客户可见文本的语义保真改写，不能读取局池、画像、工具结果后重新组织业务事实。","payload_boundary":"只提供 items[].text、generation_scope 和 action_boundary；不提供 active_games、previous_tool_results、sender_relationships、recent_conversation。","contract":"每条改写必须声明 semantic_preserved=true；如果改写新增原文没有的人数、缺口、关系或执行状态，后端丢弃该改写。","forbidden_generated_facts":["173","371","已问几个人","待审批","谁已确认","谁是组局人"]},"actual":{"problem":"旧版话术生成器拿到过多上下文，容易把表达优化做成事实补全，例如原文只说有一个1块有烟人齐开的局，却可能改写成有个173。"},"triage_status":"fixed","fix":"将 customer_visible_text_generation 改为语义保真改写器：payload 不再包含上下文和完整 action；prompt 声明唯一事实来源是 items[].text；parse 阶段要求 semantic_preserved=true，否则丢弃改写并继续审查原文。","regression_refs":[{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_customer_visible_text_generation_rejects_non_semantic_rewrite"},{"type":"pytest","id":"tests/test_agent_runtime.py::test_runtime_customer_visible_text_generation_rewrites_reply_before_review"}]}
